A crystalline geometric structure emerging from morning mist, rendered in Studio Ghibli style with soft watercolor washes and delicate linework. The crystal formation is multifaceted and translucent, catching warm amber and pale blue light, surrounded by small floating particles that sparkle like dust motes. The structure appears both organic and architectural, growing from mossy ground with tiny ferns curling at its base. Dreamy atmospheric perspective with layered clouds in peachy dawn colors behind the crystal. The scene evokes simplicity, clarity, and natural elegance—a single pure form against a gentle, expansive sky.
